comments: The song talks about the situations the band had to live from its inception told by its own members, the myths, anguishes and the worst moments of an amateur band in the music industry, from the moment of stardom to bad fortunes and issues with the label and censorship. The song has been one of the most popular of the band, the music video directed by Rogelio Sikander in Argentina at the beginning of 2004, gave the band a nomination in the Latin Grammy Awards 2005, 2 in the MTV Video Music Awards Latin America 2005 , in the 2004 crystal screen awards, four awards and two nominations at the Lo Nuestro 2006 Award.
